SALESFORCE RELEASE NOTES

Unified Analytics Experiences

Post snapshots of CRM Analytics dashboards and lenses in Slack. Add any collection created in Analytics as a component of your Lightning page.

Post from CRM Analytics to Slack
Facilitate data-driven collaboration by sharing directly from CRM Analytics to your channels in Slack. Now you can post CRM Analytics dashboards and lenses, including intelligent app dashboards. Slack recipients get a snapshot showing the latest data. Or post a link with quick action buttons that can include view details, share, subscribe, and download from Slack.
Access Any Analytics Collection in Lightning Pages
Provide analytics where your users work with embedded collections on Lightning pages. In the Lightning App Builder, you can now select any Analytics collection to be a component of your page. A collection can include CRM Analytics dashboards and lenses, Lightning reports and dashboards, and Tableau dashboards.
